                        </div>
                        <p class="text-dark">Heading to the doctor's office or medical center for appointments,
                            treatments, or check-ups? Our transportation service is here to help!. Our drivers
                            are ready to safely transport you to and from your medical appointments, ensuring you arrive
                            on time. Your health and well-being are our top priorities!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 ftco-animate mb-5">
                    <div class="py-5 px-4 bg-white shadow-sm custom-card">
                        <div class="text-center mb-3">
                            <img src="icons/disability.png" alt="icon" width="40px" class="">
                            <h5 class="text-center" style="color: #003566;"><b>personalized <br> Transportation</b></h5>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-dark"> We offer personalized transportation services for individuals who may face
                            challenges in going out due to illness, disability, or other circumstances. With our
                            specialized vehicles equipped for accessibility and our drivers dedicated to
                            providing a helping hand, you can trust us to ensure that every ride is secure, and
                            tailored to your specific needs. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 ftco-animate mb-5">
                    <div class="py-5 px-4 bg-white shadow-sm custom-card">
                        <div class="text-center mb-3">
                            <img src="icons/airport.png" alt="icon" width="30px" class="">
                            <h5 class="text-center" style="color: #003566;"><b>Airport <br> Transportation</b>
                                <h5>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-dark">Heading from or to the airport and need a ride? Look no further! Our
                            service is here to make your airport pickup and drop-off a breeze. Whether you're jetting
                            off on a vacation or returning home after a trip, our drivers will be there to
                            greet you and ensure you reach your destination on time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 ftco-animate mb-5">
                    <div class="py-5 px-4 bg-white shadow-sm custom-card">
                        <div class="text-center mb-3">
                            <img src="icons/shopping.png" alt="icon" width="30px" class="mb-3">
                            <h5 class="text-center" style="color: #003566;"><b>Shopping </b></h5>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-dark">Heading out for a shopping, but worried about finding parking or
                            carrying heavy bags? Don't stress! Our service is here to make your shopping trips a
                            breeze. Whether you're picking up groceries, shopping for clothes, or grabbing household
                            essentials, our drivers will take you to your destination comfortably.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 ftco-animate mb-5">
                    <div class="py-5 px-4 bg-white shadow-sm custom-card">
                        <div class="text-center mb-3">
                            <img src="icons/student.png" alt="icon" width="30px" class="">
                            <h5 class="text-center" style="color: #003566;"><b>Student <br> Transportation</b></h5>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-dark">Need a ride to school, soccer practice, or a friend's house? We've got you
                            covered! Our service is here to help kids get to where they need to be when parents or
                            guardians aren't available to drive. Whether it's a weekday morning or a weekend afternoon,
                            our friendly drivers will pick you up and drop you off safely and on time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
